Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspense and deduction closes the gap between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love and hatred between two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori Heiji has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He solves a mystery with Jodie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the investigation records of the cases that Detective Mouri helped solve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were stolen from the Metropolitan Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Detective Takagi really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me that the thieves are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Maybe they had a hand in this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they heard rumors that I, who was supposed to have been dead by that drug
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if they noticed something suspicious about Kogoro Mouri's deductions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if someone among the men in black found out that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi Kudo was advising Kogoro Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my disappearance coincided with the time when
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro" started, so it wouldn't surprise me if they thought it strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, rumors are rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi Kudo isn't around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one could imagine that the drug shrank me and that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still solving cases by, putting Pops to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they did see me going around solving cases behind the scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'd only think of me as a super smart kid for my age
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it hasn't been determined that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're the ones who stole the records yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... it's definite that someone is spying on Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case,\NI have a favor to ask you. Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You use me when you want and then you ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ask someone more reliable than me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... So,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you mad that I didn't tell you about the stolen records?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be mad at me, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she was there at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She? You mean Ail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she knew that somebody was snooping something around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she would refuse to go out again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I gave her my word...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And told her not to worry, because I'd would do everything I could
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to help her if things start looking bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you see, I can't have her worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, where's Haibaray
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the lab downstairs; I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't let her know about this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's not as tough as she pretends to be, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English Teacher -v-s: Renowned\NDetective of the West" Part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who stole the files sent everything back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the Metropolitan Police,\NIn a sealed envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... the culprit probably returned the files
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he or she already finished examining them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they finished examining the files, then why didn't they just throw them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would they go out of their way to send the files back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and breed more suspicion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most possible explanation is that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they are trying to relay a defiant message,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already on to all your tricks."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're trying to lure someone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in this case, the person they are trying to lure out is Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I don't get is if it's really a trap, then
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why are they doing it in such a complicated way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There're a lot of ways to lure someone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What... what are you doing here, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man called me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying that if I, your BEST FRIEND, came, I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was under the impression that\NShinichi was burdened with something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had a hard time finding a way out{from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess we're dealing with something similar to grasping clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so there's not much we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why{do you think Kudo came to tell-'you such an important thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which he hadn't told you until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came here either
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he found a very important piece of information, or because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he has found a way to counter attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, correct? Say something, will'you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You face is telling me that I hit the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, do you remember I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I had a brush with them at Haido City Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went there with that\NIittle girl named Haibara
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hunted down the old man named Pisco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Pisco have the handkerchief of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which he wasn't supposed to have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he was questioned at the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were seven suspects detained for questioning by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Pisco didn't think that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his handkerchief would be checked by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone among the other six suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who knew that he was gonna be checked first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,secretly gave Pisco the handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides\NPisco, the other six suspects were
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika Nanjo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuo Mihei,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshiharu Tahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoya Tarumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naomichi Mugikura,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Chris Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All six of them are celebrities- who appear frequently on the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is one person who announced taking a break from work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and disappeared since that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chris Vineyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The American movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chris... a second generation actress
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that clever and beautiful actress with big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only child of the famous actress,\NSharon Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked on a lot of things, buts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's the most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to think so though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I want to ask a favor of you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An internet address?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a website uploaded by fervent fans of hers wanting her to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you access the site and gather information?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her biographical data, interests or habits
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any hot topics, anything that her fans know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going to the Internet Cafe any more than\NI already have, as a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,checking out foreign websites is going to make people suspicious of me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What re you gonna do with all the information?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it may come in handy one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have somebody, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Theresa suspicious foreign woman around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be silly. No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Jodie, the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie?
