Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By a foreign woman, a boy speaking Osaka-Ben
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a little kid with glasses.
