Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'was you after all!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gosh» I'm really glad you held back from entering the room!
