Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had the front door been locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah'ilt- was locked up tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this room was locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it must be suicide II'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is what I first thought too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I saw the curtain of the bed room window
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from which Mr. Takai jumped!
