Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it just that the curtain blew outward because of the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer!
