Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is evidence that he involuntarily grabbed the curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he came close to falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would someone trying to kill himself do that?
