Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how the culprit\NIead Mr. Takai to jump from the window?
